Just as it is written,
“On account of you we are being put to death the whole day long;
we are considered as sheep for slaughter.”A quotation from Ps 44:22

But I say, Israel did not know, did they?*The negative construction in Greek anticipates a negative answer here First, Moses says,
“I will provoke you to jealousy by those who are not a nation;
by a senseless nation I will provoke you to anger.”A quotation from Deut 32:21

And Isaiah is very bold and says,
“I was found by those who did not seek me;
I became known to those who did not ask for me.”A quotation from Isa 65:1
